This paper discusses the evaluation of component systems for text summarization, which falls under the categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the construction of evaluation resources, which could potentially fall under the category of computational linguistics (cs.LG) or cybernetics (cs.CY).
